----Unit Testing----
This can be run by calling a specific target in makefile in the up-directory.

please, be noted that the testing is done using the file generated in
"solutions-output" subdirectory, so if you want to test another output file
please, make sure of the file's path.

the testing checkes the size of the board given by the user
if this size out range of 2-18 inclusive, the test failed.
